sterdam/0000018e-2d29-dc45-a7ef-6dfd89610000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙人质与哈马斯的谈判在斋月开始时陷入困境，以色列不排除达成协议的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</link><description>一位外国官员表示，双方都在互相较量。另一位人士表示，“我们的假设是最终会达成协议。”哈马斯领导人哈尼亚表示，以色列没有承诺停止战斗并允许流离失所的加沙人从南部返回北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</guid></item><item><title>美国建造的港口可以将以色列变成加沙警察部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</link><description>该港口可能会免除以色列对加沙人道主义局势的责任，但如果没有商定的授权，混乱的风险就会增加</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列核实哈马斯高级军事指挥官是否在以色列国防军对加沙的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</link><description>以色列正在检查哈马斯激进派别二号人物马鲁安·伊萨 (Maruan Issa) 是否已在袭击中身亡。 据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，美国相信以色列近期不会在拉法开展行动。阿克萨大院 ■ 加沙官员警告说，只有哈马斯才有能力监督援助物资的分配 ■ 美国推动战斗暂停两到四天，以恢复协议谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</guid></item><item><title>七名阿拉伯裔以色列男子被指控策划对犹太以色列人发动恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</link><description>这七人来自北部城市萨赫宁，据称购买武器并接受训练，目的是在战争爆发时攻击犹太公民和士兵。该小组后来由一名自称哈马斯成员的加沙人指挥</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:10:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年，阿拉伯裔以色列人的谋杀率创下历史新高。今年的步伐正在加快</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</link><description>《国土报》报道称，今年迄今已有 36 名以色列阿拉伯人被谋杀，而 2023 年同期为 31 人，受害者总数为 299 人</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 22:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼将在拉马拉宣布胜利，签署两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</link><description>以色列左派现在有机会提出一种替代刀剑生活的选择，并再次发挥作用</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公布欧洲歌唱大赛参赛作品《飓风》</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-unveils-hurricane-its-entry-for-the-eurovision-song-contest/0000018e-2a27-d682-a9df-ebaf12ed0000</link><description>这首歌由伊登·戈兰 (Eden Golan) 演唱，将代表以色列参加五月在瑞典举行的欧洲歌唱大赛。周日早些时候，一名支持巴勒斯坦的用户在网上泄露了这首歌的预录，标题是“以色列正在实施种族灭绝”</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-unveils-hurricane-its-entry-for-the-eurovision-song-contest/0000018e-2a27-d682-a9df-ebaf12ed0000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列的 GPS 干扰令黎巴嫩边境的约会应用程序陷入混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/israels-gps-jamming-confuses-dating-apps-on-lebanese-border-report-says/0000018e-29d6-d682-a9df-e9fec4370000</link><description>据 Business Insider 报道，使用 GPS 位置的应用程序受到以色列军方为阻止黎巴嫩袭击而进行的 GPS 干扰的影响。因此，2 月份出现在黎巴嫩 Tinder 上的个人资料中有 60-62% 是以色列国民</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 20:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/israels-gps-jamming-confuses-dating-apps-on-lebanese-border-report-says/0000018e-29d6-d682-a9df-e9fec4370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法律顾问称，定居者委员会没收巴勒斯坦人的牛群是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/settler-councils-confiscating-palestinians-herds-is-illegal-says-military-legal-adviser/0000018e-27e2-d1b8-a5de-e7fe17300000</link><description>以色列国防军西岸法律顾问表示，该委员会执行的章程仅适用于以色列人，不适用于巴勒斯坦人。四名巴勒斯坦牧民的代表请求以色列高等法院释放这些动物并退还理事会收取的款项</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/settler-councils-confiscating-palestinians-herds-is-illegal-says-military-legal-adviser/0000018e-27e2-d1b8-a5de-e7fe17300000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判：尽管总理要求推迟，但官员作证的日期已确定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-dates-set-for-officials-testimony-despite-pms-request-to-postpone/0000018e-2987-d7d3-abce-69afc0f10000</link><description>法官们并未正式拒绝内塔尼亚胡推迟作证的请求，但通过安排两次作证基本上否定了内塔尼亚胡的要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-dates-set-for-officials-testimony-despite-pms-request-to-postpone/0000018e-2987-d7d3-abce-69afc0f10000</guid></item><item><title>科学发现巨蛇新物种：北方绿森蚺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-10/ty-article/science-recognizes-new-species-of-giant-snake-the-northern-green-anaconda/0000018e-2909-dbcf-abee-39d967280000</link><description>事实证明，南美洲的巨型绿蛇不是一种，而是两种。在截然不同的地形中发现的多种黄色水蚺就是其中之一</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-10/ty-article/science-recognizes-new-species-of-giant-snake-the-northern-green-anaconda/0000018e-2909-dbcf-abee-39d967280000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔向以色列最高法院表示：独立警察对民主构成威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-to-israels-top-court-independent-police-is-a-danger-to-democracy/0000018e-296f-d7d3-abce-69ef196c0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔反对推翻警察隶属于国家安全部长的法律的请愿书，声称警察“独立”将使以色列变成“警察国家”</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:10:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-to-israels-top-court-independent-police-is-a-danger-to-democracy/0000018e-296f-d7d3-abce-69ef196c0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 156 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-156/0000018e-2946-dbcf-abee-39de37730000</link><description>据报道，埃及正在与哈马斯高级成员和以色列官员接触，以重启停火谈判。 ■ 以色列人质家属将出席联合国安理会有关哈马斯对以色列妇女性暴力的会议。 ■ 730 名以色列学者签署的请愿书呼吁政府“采取紧急措施防止加沙饥饿 ■ 拜登：内塔尼亚胡“对以色列的伤害大于帮助” ■ 战争结束 156 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-156/0000018e-2946-dbcf-abee-39de37730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方释放周六晚被拘留的 17 名反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/i